thread.title_full: Sportbike Track Gear reviewed by Keith Jackson

author: Keith Jackson
title: Keith Jackson
text: Can't speak to the product, itself, as yet. But STG banged out a set of tires for me, the next day. I'm just another guy- nobody special. Was very happy to get the shipment so fast, at a decent price. Love the instructional vids. Will purchase more products from STG in the future.
